Package: imaihda
Type: Package
Title: Intersectional MAIHDA Diagnostics for Health Inequality Research
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Minh Thien", "Nguyen",
           email = "nguyenminh2301@users.noreply.github.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Factory Droid", role = "ctb",
           comment = "AI-assisted code generation and testing")
  )
Description: Fast synthetic-diagnostic tools for Intersectional Multilevel
    Analysis of Individual Heterogeneity and Discriminatory Accuracy (I-MAIHDA).
    Computes Variance Partition Coefficient (VPC) and Proportional Change in
    Variance (PCV) from intersectional strata using empirical-logit
    method-of-moments estimators. Includes a simulation engine for stress-testing
    VPC/PCV sensitivity to outcome prevalence, sparse strata, and differential
    detection.
